    <author>
      <name>Xueli Zhang, Wei Miao, Junhong Chu, Ivan Png</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;b&gt;Marketing Science&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;This paper develops a dynamic structural model to investigate the tradeoff between matching efficiency and agent autonomy in the ride-hailing market.</content>
